 uw kat schoon, zuiver water drinkt dat vrij is van verontreinigingen en veilig is voor iedereen.<\/p>","text_style":"body"}}},"block_order":["template--19900162113860__7c2381c3-1795-445b-91da-9765523b1638-text-1"],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/gif_1_a6eb40af-ef25-4fa8-8597-baf965c6f38b.webp","height":"adapt","color_scheme":"background-1","section_color_scheme":"background-1","content_layout":"no-overlap","layout":"text_first","desktop_content_position":"middle","desktop_content_alignment":"center","mobile_content_alignment":"left"}},"d7112918-a6ed-4119-8565-5d4b7041284a":{"type":"rich-text","settings":{"desktop_content_position":"center","content_alignment":"center","full_width":true,"color_scheme":"background-1","padding_top":12,"padding_bottom":12}},"16947789000e7c3be1":{"type":"apps","settings":{"include_margins":true}},"169477810286cbda2b":{"type":"apps","settings":{"include_margins":true}},"1694778916ae6d13bb":{"type":"apps","settings":{"include_margins":true}},"7ead9d52-a3ce-4f63-9e00-e5fbe252c5a8":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"9bd8fb44-fa40-449d-be77-8f37af118496":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<h4>De perfecte oplossing<\/h4><p>Het donzige, zachte hondenbed van Roolo is in samenwerking met diertherapeuten ontwikkeld om de <strong>gewrichten<\/strong> van je viervoeter optimaal <strong>te<\/strong> <strong>ontlasten, angst te verminderen en je huisdier het best mogelijke slaapcomfort te bieden.<\/strong><\/p>","text_style":"body"}}},"block_order":["9bd8fb44-fa40-449d-be77-8f37af118496"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Scherm_afbeelding_2023-11-14_om_16.41.59.png","height":"adapt","color_scheme":"background-1","section_color_scheme":"background-1","content_layout":"no-overlap","layout":"text_first","desktop_content_position":"middle","desktop_content_alignment":"center","mobile_content_alignment":"left"}},"af19ca60-4102-40cc-8748-150b1134b815":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"template--20144669000004